Features of the Page:

1. Header Section:

Contains a site title (h1) and a navigation bar (nav) with links to key pages like Home, Sign Up, Login, and Contact.



2. Hero Section:

Welcoming message with a call-to-action button leading to the signup page.



3. Footer Section:

Displays copyright information.



4. Responsive Design:

The layout is mobile-friendly and adapts to different screen sizes.




Customization:

Replace the content (like the website title or tagline) with your actual details.

Add more sections or features, such as a gallery, testimonials, or product highlights, as required.

